{"tid":2417543,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇返工兄弟試過屙屎嗰陣聽到隔離嗰隔屙屎同事喺到傻笑/講嘢？","createTime":"2021-02-22T03:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T04:06:33.000Z","uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"68a12ad134aaaaa1eecffb6dd2a025106276ae74","tid":2417543,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T03:30:27.000Z","msg":"返工屙屎廁格有限，大大話話都同所有同事做過鄰居<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但有冇試過坐坐下發現隔離鄰居無啦啦瘋狂傻笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n心諗返工返到個人傻撚咗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦試過聽到有鄰居自言自語，重覆咗三次：「今年加人工、今年加人工、今年加人工。」之後自己又喺道笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最詭異都係出返去做嘢個陣，佢個人又正正常常<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟公司廁所入面係咪有咩結界<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e19d45dbaeb4cceb9e1fbf923ab32e21e2cddf","tid":2417543,"uid":301529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T03:33:13.000Z","msg":"聽到有𠽌𠽌聲"},{"pid":"e5290cabe2141d34da8a2b9e1fd4a80d78de8fc0","tid":2417543,"uid":309553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T03:33:52.000Z","msg":"試過喺女廁聽到有人討論點殺人"},{"pid":"a88d019fecfe6ede3ead9ff18cabba55ddbe3f5f","tid":2417543,"uid":189246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T03:50:19.000Z","msg":"係咪用緊電話咋"},{"pid":"8c312191962d3e0733722d7a54478e8ebd07803c","tid":2417543,"uid":8308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T03:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7354ad347a0b34dd4a78d3b8339279d24693b27f","tid":2417543,"uid":238340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T03:57:13.000Z","msg":"係人都會自言自語，同埋傻笑。<br />\n可惜佢係唔適當嘅地方做，俾你聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80887964a2962b24c1aef9fbc4028cb0eaa4a713","tid":2417543,"uid":130121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:04:32.000Z","msg":"記得以前仲讀緊書果時<br />\n同個fd喺尿兜屙緊尿<br />\n<br />\n突然間聽到廁格有人肚屙<br />\n條友屙到好似燒炮仗咁<br />\n<br />\n開頭我地忍笑 最尾忍唔到爆笑咗出黎<br />\n果時幾驚比人打 即刻洗完手跑出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65fb90111b6032f408fe4c281a98430fced41eb","tid":2417543,"uid":94241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"可能人地錄音要SEND出去者"}]}